## **ENGLISH VERSION** 
*For informational purposes only*

### PRIVACY POLICY
**Effective Date:** September 5, 2025  
**Data Controller:** Marek SZEWCZYK  
**Domains:** neuroatypowi.cloudflareaccess.com, neuroatypowi.pl.eu.org

#### 1. OVERVIEW
Mr. Marek SZEWCZYK operates technological infrastructure encompassing internet domains and security systems. This privacy policy establishes principles for personal data processing in compliance with GDPR, international legislation, and industry best practices. We process personal data of domain group members to the full extent necessary for security and service functionality.

#### 2. PERSONAL DATA PROCESSED
We process the following data categories:
- **Login credentials:** user identifiers, passwords, authentication tokens
- **Technical specifications:** hardware, software, operating system information
- **Security monitoring data:** access logs, network traffic analysis, threat detection
- **User account data:** profiles within neuroatypowi.pl.eu.org infrastructure
- **Access information:** IP addresses, timestamps, geolocation data
- **Vulnerability analysis:** security scanning results, malware detection

#### 3. PROCESSING PURPOSES AND LEGAL BASIS
We process data based on legitimate interests, user consent, and contract performance:
- **Security management:** protection against cyberattacks, malware, intrusions
- **System functionality:** service access provisioning, account management
- **Legal compliance:** fulfilling data security obligations
- **Technology development:** performance and reliability optimization

#### 4. THIRD-PARTY SERVICES UTILIZED
**Cloudflare Zero Trust** (free plan):
- Remote access protection (RMM security)
- Network traffic and DNS processing
- DDoS attack protection
- Privacy Policy: https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/

**Action1 RMM** (free version):
- Remote system monitoring capabilities
- Device configuration management
- Infrastructure security analysis
- Privacy Policy: https://www.action1.com/privacy-policy/

**VirusTotal** (free version):
- **WARNING:** Uploaded files become publicly accessible
- File and URL security analysis
- Security community data sharing
- Privacy Notice: https://cloud.google.com/terms/secops/privacy-notice

**Wazuh Server** (Oracle Cloud Free Tier):
- Open-source SIEM platform
- Security log analysis capabilities
- File integrity monitoring
- DPA: https://wazuh.com/legal-resources/data-protection-agreement/

**Google Cloud Run** (free tier):
- Web link description application with APA formatting
- DOI link generation and QR codes
- Privacy Notice: https://cloud.google.com/terms/cloud-privacy-notice

**Microsoft Entra** (Azure AD free features):
- Identity and access management
- Windows user authentication
- Group and permission management
- Privacy Statement: https://privacy.microsoft.com/en-us/privacystatement

#### 5. DATA TRANSFERS
Data may be transferred outside EEA based on:
- European Commission adequacy decisions
- Standard Contractual Clauses (SCCs)
- EU-US Data Privacy Framework certifications
- All transfers include appropriate GDPR safeguards

#### 6. DATA SUBJECT RIGHTS
You have the following rights under GDPR:
- **Access:** request copies of processed data
- **Rectification:** correct inaccurate information
- **Erasure:** request data deletion ("right to be forgotten")
- **Portability:** receive data in structured format
- **Objection:** object to processing activities
- **Restriction:** request processing limitations

#### 7. DATA SECURITY
We implement technical and organizational security measures:
- End-to-end data encryption in transit and at rest
- Role-based access control systems
- Regular security audits and assessments
- Real-time monitoring and alerting
- Comprehensive backup and recovery procedures

#### 8. RETENTION PERIODS
Data retention periods by category:
- **Login credentials:** 12 months
- **Security logs:** 24 months
- **Account data:** account lifetime plus 6 months
- **Breach data:** 5 years per regulatory requirements

#### 9. GOOGLE CONSENT MODE V2
We implement Google Consent Mode V2 complying with DMA and GDPR:
- Cookie consent management framework
- Advertising and analytics storage controls
- Privacy-preserving conversion modeling
- Granular user control mechanisms

#### 10. CONTACT AND COMPLAINTS
**Data Controller:** Marek SZEWCZYK  
**Email:** rodo@neuroatypowi.pl.eu.org  
**Supervisory Authority:** Relevant data protection authority  
**Complaint Rights:** File complaints with supervisory authorities for rights violations

